00:10:57,703 --> 00:11:00,604
- Will you hire her now?
- Oh!

147
00:11:00,673 --> 00:11:03,870
<i>Uh... how long</i>
<i>have you boys been playing?</i>

148
00:11:03,943 --> 00:11:06,104
