175
00:12:20,786 --> 00:12:22,947
- [Sighs]
- <i>For now.</i>

176
00:12:23,022 --> 00:12:25,650
- Thank you very much.
- <i>But even if it works out,</i>

177
00:12:25,724 --> 00:12:28,318
