a permanent position for you.

178
00:12:28,394 --> 00:12:30,328
That's okay. Anything is okay.
That's great.

179
00:12:30,396 --> 00:12:32,830
- I have already planned out
the whole term.
- Oh, thank you very much.

180
00:12:32,898 --> 00:12:34,661
- [Laughing]
- Yes!
- <i>There is no room for this.</i>

181
00:12:34,733 --> 00:12:37,634
<i>Besides, where are you gonna</i>
<i>find money for violins?</i>

182
00:12:37,703 --> 00:12:40,672
Oh, you need violins?

183
00:12:40,739 --> 00:12:45,972
- [Scoffs]
- I have violins. I have 50 violins.

184
00:12:46,045 --> 00:12:49,981
Thank you very much.
Nice to meet you, Mr...

185
00:12:50,049 --> 00:12:52,779
- Rouche.
- Rouche. Th-Thank you.

186
00:12:53,018 --> 00:12:55,486
- Okay. Lucy?
- <i>[Children Chattering]</i>

187
00:12:55,554 --> 00:12:58,648
<i>[Boy] Hey, let's go get one!</i>
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

188
00:12:58,724 --> 00:13:01,420
