Give it to me, now!

189
00:13:01,494 --> 00:13:04,088
- Come on, I want one! Come on!
- Please, don't open...

190
00:13:04,163 --> 00:13:07,394
Don't open the cases, okay, everybody?
Don't open the cases.

191
00:13:07,466 --> 00:13:09,058
- [Imitating Gunfire]
- <i>[Roberta] No guns.</i>

192
00:13:09,135 --> 00:13:13,094
Okay, now...
listen to me, please!

193
00:13:13,172 --> 00:13:16,608
- <i>[Girl] I don't like this one.</i>
- No, no! Please, keep them closed!

194
00:13:16,675 --> 00:13:20,406
Stop it, you two.
You two, what did I just say?

195
00:13:20,479 --> 00:13:23,710
Stop! No, no, please, don't. Don't.
No, no, no. No, no, no, please.

196
00:13:23,782 --> 00:13:25,716
<i>just put them back</i>
<i>in the case, all right?</i>

197
00:13:25,784 --> 00:13:30,744
Who's plucking?
Who's plucking my violin? Hey!

198
00:13:30,823 --> 00:13:32,950
Please, will you put it back
in the case right now?

199
00:13:33,025 --> 00:13:37,394
<i>Good. Okay. So today I'm going</i>
<i>to be dividing you all up...</i>

200
00:13:37,463 --> 00:13:41,524
- ♪♪ [Drumming, Humming]
- <i>into five different classes.</i>

201
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:46,299
♪♪ [Continues Drumming,
Humming]

202
00:13:47,940 --> 00:13:50,875
Hello.
Come with me.

203
00:13:53,045 --> 00:13:57,311
You're gonna be the first student
who is not in my violin class, okay?

204
00:13:57,383 --> 00:14:00,147
<i>I want you to go</i>
<i>to the office right now.</i>

205
00:14:00,219 --> 00:14:02,414
Right now.
Out, out, out.

206
00:14:02,488 --> 00:14:04,683
Go on, go on, go on.
Out, out.

207
00:14:06,325 --> 00:14:11,422
- <i>[Door Opening]</i>
- Who wants to be next?

208
00:14:11,497 --> 00:14:15,263
Who wants to be kicked out
of my class?

209
00:14:15,334 --> 00:14:17,427
<i>Are you raising</i>
<i>your hand...</i>

210
00:14:17,503 --> 00:14:19,937
- because you want to be kicked out?
- <i>[Boy] Yeah.</i>

211
00:14:20,005 --> 00:14:23,600
- Wh-Why?
- I don't want to learn
about no stupid violins.

212
00:14:23,676 --> 00:14:27,510
- Man, violin's for wimps.
- [Class Laughing]

213
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:30,242
- Who told you that?
- <i>[Boy] Nobody.</i>

214
00:14:30,316 --> 00:14:32,250
- I just know.
- <i>[Roberta] What's your name?</i>

215
00:14:32,318 --> 00:14:34,115
- DeSean.
- <i>Well, DeSean...</i>

216
00:14:34,186 --> 00:14:37,246
you didn't give me
a good enough reason, so you're staying.

217
00:14:42,027 --> 00:14:44,894
Anybody else?

218
00:14:48,567 --> 00:14:52,298
Very nice.
Everybody be quiet.

219
00:14:52,371 --> 00:14:54,839
<i>I'm gonna hand out</i>
<i>the violins.</i>

220
00:14:54,907 --> 00:14:57,467
