793
00:51:16,186 --> 00:51:18,780
if you have some needs
that I don't meet,

794
00:51:18,855 --> 00:51:21,881
you would go and have them
met by somebody else?

795
00:51:21,958 --> 00:51:24,620
[Laughing]

796
00:51:24,694 --> 00:51:29,961
