to somebody else?

804
00:51:50,554 --> 00:51:52,988
In theory... yes.

805
00:51:54,558 --> 00:51:56,492
"In theory"?

806
00:51:56,560 --> 00:51:58,494
Wait a second.
Wait, wait.

807
00:51:58,562 --> 00:52:00,826
Wh-What happened here?

808
00:52:00,897 --> 00:52:02,888
