824
00:52:50,714 --> 00:52:54,912
I don't care.
Just go do it, now. Go. Go.

825
00:52:54,985 --> 00:52:57,249
I want to go to Brian's!

826
00:52:57,320 --> 00:52:59,982
<i>[Roberta]</i>
<i>Stop whining...</i>

827
00:53:00,056 --> 00:53:02,320
